      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i mean... they're both just sleep aids, right? one is natural and the other is just a pill. i'm not even taking any other meds or drinking alcohol, so it shouldn't be a big deal. i just really need to sleep tonight and im worried if i only take the ambien it might not be enough. won't the melatonin just make it work a little more effectively? it's not like they're conflicting or anything.",
